DynDNS,com,is,an,all,in,one,managed,DNS,hosting,solution,for,top,level,domains,ie,www,yourwebsite,com,Their,DNS,Update,API,is,also,known,as,the,Members,NIC,Update,API,and,is,used,to,update,the,IP,addresses,of,dynamic,DNS,hostnames,DynDNS,designed,and,created,the,specification,prior,to,which,has,become,the,standard,update,mechanism,for,other,DNS,providers,The,API,works,over,HTTPS,and,HTTP